title: About
text: Hello, world! My name is Rong Wan. I’m a Master of Data Science (MDS) student at the University of British Columbia (UBC). I’m passionate about leveraging data to uncover insights and solve real-world problems. My focus is on applying advanced data science techniques, including machine learning and statistical analysis, to diverse datasets. As I continue my journey, I’m excited to contribute to the field and collaborate on innovative data-driven projects!
